00:41:40.520 --> 00:41:43.280
I did do a little bit of
shorthand, because I didn't

00:41:43.280 --> 00:41:44.400
want to do too many caveats.

00:41:44.400 --> 00:41:45.210
You're absolutely correct.

00:41:45.210 --> 00:41:47.810
There are a few-- very few,
fewer than you'd think--

00:41:47.810 --> 00:41:50.230
particles that are their
own anti-particles.

00:41:50.230 --> 00:41:53.630
A photon is its own
anti-particle, as

00:41:53.630 --> 00:41:56.030
