00:42:04.830 --> 00:42:06.560
particle and anti-particle
collide,

00:42:06.560 --> 00:42:08.150
it creates two photons.

00:42:08.150 --> 00:42:12.100
And there is no distinguishing
between which one's the

00:42:12.100 --> 00:42:14.320
